{"tid":1210642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"所有冇登記做選民，都係有份賣港","createTime":"2019-06-12T14:09:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T10:47:04.000Z","uid":10806,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b1ff3930c6077cb8a7bcd248c8c1cb95d5aaa43b","tid":1210642,"uid":10806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:09:01.000Z","msg":"而今日有份去示威<br />\n而冇投票冇登記做選民都有份賣港<br />\n我係幫兇<br />\n昨晚見到民主黨議員出發去金鐘<br />\n幫被警犬查證嘅年青人<br />\n我好感動<br />\n<br />\n今日示威係亡羊補牢<br />\n我地冇投票冇做選民<br />\n點解夠票通過二讀三讀<br />\n係我地做成<br />\n對不起，今日嘅義士，勇士<br />\n我欠咗你地"},{"pid":"da0a696774793e7e2584b7e670fc6290cae9287f","tid":1210642,"uid":5523,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:09:59.000Z","msg":"投左la<br />\ndq埋tim"},{"pid":"01ca3760b535d6ccb2481b040084c41ac97f78b5","tid":1210642,"uid":10806,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"da0a696774793e7e2584b7e670fc6290cae9287f","tid":1210642,"uid":5523,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:09:59.000Z","msg":"投左la<br />\ndq埋tim"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:11:45.000Z","msg":"如果多啲人投票，我不相信老共，可以dp再多嘅議席"},{"pid":"22c15d4204810f59bf924ee715c4eac49e82d0d8","tid":1210642,"uid":4942,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:16:00.000Z","msg":"各位！！ 選民登記7月2日截止！！<br />\n<br />\n未登記快d登記！！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fvrsubmit.htm&d=P3WkhlyCj4fBe8yrVMQ2y9OJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=16474186\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/vrsubmit.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2541558b1f4477e4c3ca4661841d14f9b739324d","tid":1210642,"uid":163758,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"01ca3760b535d6ccb2481b040084c41ac97f78b5","tid":1210642,"uid":10806,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"da0a696774793e7e2584b7e670fc6290cae9287f","tid":1210642,"uid":5523,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score"